.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, iced-tea, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, climbing, sailing, cycling
4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, mouse, rabbit
1. the person drinking cola is not the person who's sport is cycling##6
2. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the person who's sport is surfing##7
3. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person who's sport is climbing and the person drinking fanta##7
5. the person drinking fanta is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the mouse is the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta  | cola | iced-tea | lemonade |
| Sport   | cycling | sailing  | climbing  | surfing    |
| Pet           | rabbit | cat  | horse    | mouse    |

