.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, drama, martial-arts, scientific
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, magic-tricks, photography
There are 4 different nationalities: british, chinese, colombian, egyptian
1. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
3. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##5
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
7. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the british##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre      | scientific     | martial-arts | time-travel        | drama       |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | chess    | filmmaking | photography |
| Nationality   | egyptian     | chinese  | british    | colombian   |

