.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, librarian, musician, photographer
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, baccarat, aristoff, tiparillo
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, quad-bike, train
1. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
2. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
3. the siglo-smoker is between the tiparillo-smoker and the aristoff-smoker##2
4. the doctor is somewhere to the right of the musician##5
5. the person driving the train is in an even position##4
6. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##5
7. the musician is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the airplane##7
8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
9. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the siglo-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |      4       |
| Job         | librarian | musician | doctor    | photographer |
| Cigar         | baccarat      | tiparillo | siglo       | aristoff         |
| Transport   | quad-bike | train    | motorbike | airplane     |

