.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-11::.
House: tower, cottage, colonial, modern
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indonesian, mexican, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, guinea-pig, rabbit
1. the modern house is on the right of the colonial house##1
2. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the indonesian##5
3. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
4. the cottage house is between the indonesian and the owner of the rabbit##2
5. the nigerian is not the colonial house##6
6. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
7. the owner of the rabbit is the mexican##1
8. the indonesian is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
9. the nigerian is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the tower house##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| House   | tower   | cottage        | colonial        | modern   |
| Nationality   | mexican | nigerian   | indonesian | french |
| Pet           | rabbit  | guinea-pig | fish       | ferret |

