5. the person eating corn is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
6. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
8. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the person watching epic movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
