6. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not the person who's sport is skiing##6
9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's sport is badminton##1

